flowchart TD
    Start([CLI Entry: main.py]) --> ArgParse[Parse Arguments<br/>--decode, --output<br/>--refresh-mitre<br/>--include-secondary-techniques]
    ArgParse --> ReadInput{Input Source?}
    ReadInput -->|Arguments| JoinArgs[Join command args]
    ReadInput -->|stdin| ReadStdin[Read from stdin]
    JoinArgs --> Pipeline
    ReadStdin --> Pipeline
    
    Pipeline[translate_command<br/>pipeline.py] --> DecodeCheck{--decode flag?}
    
    DecodeCheck -->|Yes| DetectEnc[detect_encoding_types<br/>decoder.py]
    DetectEnc --> DecodeCmd[decode_command<br/>decoder.py]
    DecodeCmd --> DecodeResult{Decoded?}
    DecodeResult -->|Yes| UseDecoded[Use decoded command<br/>Store decode_info]
    DecodeResult -->|No| UseOriginal1[Use original command]
    DecodeCheck -->|No| UseOriginal2[Use original command]
    
    UseDecoded --> Normalize
    UseOriginal1 --> Normalize
    UseOriginal2 --> Normalize
    
    Normalize[normalize_command<br/>parser.py] --> DetectPrimary[detect_t1059<br/>detector.py]
    
    DetectPrimary --> MatchIndicators1[_match_indicators<br/>evidences from INDICATOR_DB]
    MatchIndicators1 --> ScoreConf1[score_confidence<br/>evidence-based scoring]
    ScoreConf1 --> SecCheck{include_secondary<br/>techniques?}
    
    SecCheck -->|Yes| GetCache[get_attackcti_cache<br/>mitre.py]
    GetCache --> DetectSec[detect_secondary_techniques<br/>detector.py]
    DetectSec --> DetectT1218[detect_t1218<br/>LOLBins detection]
    DetectT1218 --> MatchIndicators2[_match_indicators]
    MatchIndicators2 --> ScoreConf2[score_confidence]
    ScoreConf2 --> DetectT1027[detect_t1027<br/>Obfuscation detection]
    DetectT1027 --> MatchIndicators3[_match_indicators]
    MatchIndicators3 --> ScoreConf3[score_confidence]
    ScoreConf3 --> MergeDetections
    
    SecCheck -->|No| MergeDetections[Merge all detections]
    
    MergeDetections --> BuildOutput[build_output<br/>output.py]
    BuildOutput --> EnrichDet[_enrich_detections<br/>Add metadata from METADATA_DB]
    EnrichDet --> DedupeEv[_dedupe_evidence]
    DedupeEv --> AddDecodeInfo{decode_info<br/>available?}
    
    AddDecodeInfo -->|Yes| AddDecodeMeta[Add decode_info to output]
    AddDecodeInfo -->|No| FinalOutput
    AddDecodeMeta --> FinalOutput
    
    FinalOutput[Final JSON Output] --> OutputCheck{--output flag?}
    OutputCheck -->|Yes| SaveFile[Save to data/results/<br/>with timestamp]
    OutputCheck -->|No| PrintStdout[Print to stdout]
    
    SaveFile --> End([End])
    PrintStdout --> End
    
    style Start fill:#e1f5e1
    style End fill:#ffe1e1
    style Pipeline fill:#e1e5ff
    style Normalize fill:#fff4e1
    style DetectPrimary fill:#ffe1f5
    style DetectSec fill:#ffe1f5
    style BuildOutput fill:#e1f5ff
    style FinalOutput fill:#f5e1ff